                  %h2 Source code
                  %p 
                    Source .tar.gz files can be found here:
                    %a{:href => 'https://github.com/performancecopilot/pcp/releases'} PCP source
                  %p
                    Git clone from the
                    %a{:href => 'https://github.com/performancecopilot/pcp'} PCP repository
                  %br
                  %p
                    Grafana plugin:
                    %a{:href => 'https://github.com/performancecopilot/grafana-pcp'} git://github.com/performancecopilot/grafana-pcp.git
                  %p
                    Ansible roles:
                    %a{:href => 'https://github.com/performancecopilot/ansible-pcp'} git://github.com/performancecopilot/ansible-pcp.git
                  %p
                    Java instrumentation:
                    %a{:href => 'https://github.com/performancecopilot/parfait'} git://github.com/performancecopilot/parfait.git
                  %p
                    PDF graph converter:
                    %a{:href => 'https://github.com/performancecopilot/pcp2pdf'} git://github.com/performancecopilot/pcp2pdf.git

